General.Name: Icape Holding
General.Description: Icape Holding S.A. engages in the manufacture and sale of printed circuit boards (PCBs) and technical parts worldwide. It offers single- and double-sided, aluminum, multilayer, HDI, back panel, flexible, semi- and rigid-flex, heavy copper, and RF/microwave PCBs, as well as IC substrate boards; and technical parts, such as cables and connectors, adapters, transformers and coils, keypads, batteries, displays, plastic and silicone products, prototypes, and remotes. The company serves business, telecommunications, automotive, connected objects, home automation, e-mobility, medical, power, multimedia, aerospace, metering, railway, internet of things, and lighting industries. It also sells its products online through www.icape-shop.com. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Fontenay-aux-Roses, France.
